  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Do you wish there were more parkour games like rooftops and alleys, SWIFT STRIDERS is a new parkour game similar to rooftops and alleys. It has vaults, flips, beam jumping, climbing and more. There are multiple maps to play and even a bodycam effect for hyper realistic parkour. There are also multiple characters to choose from, which use unreal engine 5 meta-humans</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3341100/extras/6e10439e6bc17e3305951d3f2d326e9e.avif?t=1750947426\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3341100/extras_big/6e10439e6bc17e3305951d3f2d326e9e.avif?t=1750947426 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SWIFT STRIDERS is a parkour game using unreal engine 5 latest technologies like unreal engine 5 new motion matching for smooth parkour vaults and actions it also uses motion warping for custom vaults like tic tac, kong, ect.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3341100/extras/92bdad230748445ed2ec2f843dd9dc17.poster.avif?t=1750947426\" width=700 height=700 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3341100/extras/92bdad230748445ed2ec2f843dd9dc17.webm?t=1750947426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GAME FEATUERS</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i>Parkour</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> Freerunning</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> Tricking System</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> Free Roam</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> Multiple Maps</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> Third and First Person Camera</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> Ragdoll/Bail Button</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Slow-motion Button</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Music</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>realistic bodycam effect</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>realistic graphics</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3341100/extras/9c82176069315109a6017214077980dd.poster.avif?t=1750947426\" width=700 height=700 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3341100/extras/9c82176069315109a6017214077980dd.webm?t=1750947426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NOTES</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >if you have a problem with the performance change the resolution to borderless and change resolution scale down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are a few bugs please don't be to harsh in the reviews as the game is free and i am trying my best thanks :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >this game isn't a fan made <strong>rooftops and alleys<i> </i></strong>game but is heavily inspired of it so thanks to <strong>rooftops and alleys</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
